_sText:
edit: fixed version is up

My first map, so go easy on me :)

Averagely sized, difficulty is between easy to medium.

Features:

 - A regular bhop and a Mpbhop part.

 - 6 bhop levels

 - BHLJ - from 300 to 500 units

 - 4 playable songs in the end of the map.

 - Spritetrail deagles in the end of both the bhop part and the bhlj parts.

 - 3 dimensional skybox.



Should you discover any bugs in the map, please leave a comment below and I'll fix it.

Hope you like the map   ~insane
